Class StoreSinkWriteImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.paimon.flink.sink.StoreSinkWriteImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StoreSinkWrite
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AsyncLookupSinkWrite, GlobalFullCompactionSinkWrite

    public class StoreSinkWriteImpl
extends Object
implements StoreSinkWrite
    Default implementation of StoreSinkWrite. This writer does not have states.

      • replace

        public void replace(FileStoreTable newTable)
             throws Exception
        Description copied from interface: StoreSinkWrite
        Replace the internal TableWriteImpl with the one provided by newWriteProvider. The state of the old TableWriteImpl will also be transferred to the new TableWriteImpl by TableWriteImpl.checkpoint() and TableWriteImpl.restore(List).

        Currently, this method is only used by CDC sinks because they need to deal with schema changes. TableWriteImpl with the new schema will be provided by newWriteProvider.

        Specified by:
        replace in interface StoreSinkWrite
        Throws:
        Exception
